name: Baby Hazel Doctor Play
description:
Baby Hazel Doctor Play is available in a bundle of 5 Baby Hazel Doctor Games. Download now.

Kids can play Baby Hazel Doctor Play game for free.

Today Baby Hazel and Mom are going to the shopping mall. Baby Hazel is so excited because she thinks Mom will buy a new toy for her. What if Hazel chooses an expensive toy? Do you think Mom will buy it for her? Mom says that anything for her million dollar princess. Wow! Mom has bought a doctor’s play set to her princess. Want to play this new toy with Baby Hazel? Join Baby Hazel in playing Doctor’s play set and help her cure teddy bear from sickness.
